#include<stdio.h>
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;

int main(){
    ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);
    unsigned long long int t,n;
    scanf("%llu",&t);
    for(;t>0;t--){
        scanf("%llu",&n);
        if(n==1 || n==10 || n==100 || n==1000 || n==10000 || n==100000)
            printf("NO\n");
        else
            printf("YES\n");
    }
    return 0;
}
